&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join the Team at Stress-Free Auto Care: Where Your Skills and Passion Drive Success!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stress Free Auto Care is redefining the auto repair experience by delivering exceptional service with honesty, transparency, and convenience. Our mission is simple: make auto care a stress-free, trustworthy experience for everyone. Join us on this exciting journey and play a pivotal role in reshaping the automotive service industry!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Product Developer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Systems &amp;amp; Operational Applications | Stress-Free Auto Care&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Stress-Free Auto Care&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.stressfree.com/?utm_source=chatgpt.com&quot;&gt; Stress-Free Auto Care&lt;/a&gt;, we are building internally developed operational software designed specifically for modern automotive service operations. Our platform combines shop management systems, workflow automation, customer communication, operational analytics, and AI-assisted tooling into a unified ecosystem used by both frontline employees and customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As we continue scaling the platform across live production environments, we are looking for a highly capable Product Engineer to help rapidly build, improve, and operationalize AI-driven applications across the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly cross-functional role that sits at the intersection of product, operations, AI systems, and real-world execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a traditional software engineering role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are not looking for someone who has spent their entire career purely as an engineer. We are looking for a highly intelligent technical generalist who enjoys solving operational problems, rapidly building solutions with AI tools, and working directly alongside end users in live environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be working directly with the CEO at a venture capital backed and fast growing company. The ideal candidate is highly adaptable, execution-oriented, and capable of figuring things out quickly across multiple domains.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates with experience from top-tier consulting firms, financial institutions, hedge funds, or similarly analytical environments may be especially strong fits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is best suited for someone who thrives in fast-moving, ambiguous, and highly iterative environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role fuses product, engineering, and design, enabled by AI&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and improve internal operational applications using modern AI development tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Observe real-world operational workflows and identify inefficiencies or usability challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rapidly prototype, test, and deploy workflow improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with frontline shop teams to improve operational usability and system adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate operational problems into scalable technical solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in AI workflow optimization and prompt engineering initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support rapid iteration cycles across deployed systems and operational platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve usability, reliability, and scalability across internal applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with leadership and operational teams to continuously improve platform functionality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Projects may include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shop management systems,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Finance-related applications,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HR applications,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operational tracking tools&lt;/li&gt;
