&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join the Team at Stress-Free Auto Care: Where Your Skills and Passion Drive Success!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stress Free Auto Care is redefining the auto repair experience by delivering exceptional service with honesty, transparency, and convenience. Our mission is simple: make auto care a stress-free, trustworthy experience for everyone. Join us on this exciting journey and play a pivotal role in reshaping the automotive service industry!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stress-Free Auto Care is a modern, tech-enabled shop that believes taking care of your car should be an easy and stress-free experience. We’re seeking an energetic, positive-minded Automotive General Manager who embraces challenges with enthusiasm and prioritizes guest satisfaction above all else.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation: $100,000 - $120,000 Base + ($20,000 - $30,000 bonus + 5% profit sharing)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PTO/Sick &amp;amp; (6) Annual Paid Holidays&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Medical, Dental &amp;amp; Vision Insurance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;401(k) Matching&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
